snippet.title: Fate/Grand Order VR feat. Mash Kyrielight Trailer
snippet.description:
Immerse yourself in the brand new Fate/Grand Order VR Drama coming February 26, 2019!

Experience another chapter of the hit mobile RPG, Fate/Grand Order, like never before with the Fate/Grand Order VR feat. Mash Kyrielight! Dive into virtual reality and join your faithful Demi-Servant, Mash Kyrielight, on a new VR adventure! Brought to you by TYPE-MOON, DELiGHTWORKS, and Aniplex, Fate/Grand Order VR is a brand new immersive FGO experience only available on PlayStation®!

For more information, please visit the official website: https://vr.fate-go.us/
